{"tid":1879380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙豐：一名員工家屬被確診新型肺炎 正接受政府隔離","createTime":"2020-02-14T07:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T07:58:36.000Z","uid":44562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7edbbc72e9bd7f6ff38b61f1d7db08e6e0023c06","tid":1879380,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90-%E5%90%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%A2%AB%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%AD%A3%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2-063200251.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590-%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259E%258B%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2-063200251.html&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=706c37cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90-%E5%90%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%A2%AB%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%AD%A3%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2-063200251.html</a><br />\n<br />\n滙豐就有關一名員工感染新型冠狀病毒肺炎作出回應指，昨天晚上得悉一名員工的家屬被確診新型肺炎，該員工與被確診的家屬曾有緊密接觸，現時正接受政府的隔離和醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐指，在過去14日内，該員工沒有接觸客戶，並自本月12日已在家中隔離。該員工在1月30至31日及2月3日，於滙豐中環總行大廈14樓上班，及在2月4至11日於將軍澳辦事處2樓上班，而這兩樓層並非用作接代客戶。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐表示，該員工的座位及附近的空間已徹底清潔和消毒，而公共空間，例如茶水間都包括在內。滙豐強調十分重視設施日常的清潔和衛生，整座辦工大樓會繼續定時清潔。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐指出，為安全起見，正聯絡可能與該員工有緊密接觸的員工，並要求他們在家隔離14天。滙豐並呼籲員工注重個人衛生。如有身體不適，應留家休息或馬上求診。所有香港員工在可行的情況下亦可留在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐又指，會繼續跟進這位員工的情況，以及聽取衛生當局和專家的意見。如有需要會適當地加強防疫措施。"},{"pid":"a9e4f3baec58f2c8de3bb55296a35b27b23e32c1","tid":1879380,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b2809061423e8e0c0a28654dcbb513e1f1ae03","tid":1879380,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b2ba14351a11131b6a335f1b190f74459bb1b5","tid":1879380,"uid":132999,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:27:53.000Z","msg":"啲報應引黎得幾快喎"},{"pid":"8c909ff75a8815b92491252a1681d58980c0bad8","tid":1879380,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"還星火錢啦"},{"pid":"12f6a9ea2bd91f829c17ec73da7caf2950bb2b3c","tid":1879380,"uid":3146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c909ff75a8815b92491252a1681d58980c0bad8","tid":1879380,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"還星火錢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"一陣又有人衝出黎話匯豐員工好黃<br />\n就黎連門口隻獅子都好黃"},{"pid":"89cddc88111e0f22b213ef01958cde583f497f99","tid":1879380,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"前線燒隻獅子終於都有用啦<br />\n病菌 直搗黃龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a4caa27c8169ab6a8c59274d393940fa778383","tid":1879380,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"政府今日先話：如檢疫後沒有確疫，應扣除年假。<br />\n<br />\n咁俾政府檢都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b29135764710c632708f1a10e57500c9e321bf9","tid":187938